![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1578271540709-SUPZZH5Q8TKN4O56ZRSA/image-asset.jpeg?format=original)

It is December 18th 2019. We are experiencing every podcast we'eve ever done simultaneously. This one in particular though is about a thermodynamic miracle. The miracle was the fact that anyone could make a satisfying sequel to Alan Moore's Watchmen graphic novel let alone one that will have us talking for years to come! Join us in this **LINEAR** look at all of the events of the 2019 smash hit Watchmen on HBO. Click [**HERE**](https://slate.com/culture/2019/12/watchmen-timeline-chronological-hbo-lindelof.html "Here") for Slate.com's comprehensive Watchmen timeline

If you can, please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the one stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
Send us feedback at **ComicBookClique@Gmail.com!** You Are Worthy! 

